MOST USEFUL
    du -sh *
      1,2G	  app
      13M	    bin
      127M	  boot
    
    du -sh app/ bin/
      1,2G	  app/
      13M	    bin/
IMPORTANT OPTIONS
    -s 
        - summarize: loop through directory, summarize sizes and output only the sizes of the specified files
    -h
        - show sizes in human readable measures
